# Expected failures for the tuf-conformance suite, one test name per line.
#
# The suite marks these as xfail(strict=True): a listed test that *passes*
# will FAIL the run, so keep this list tight and accurate. Lines that don't
# match a test name (like these comments) are ignored.
#
# This list is curated from the conformance job's uploaded JSON report
# (`tuf-conformance-results`). Until it reflects a real run, the conformance
# job in `.github/workflows/tuf-conformance.yml` is non-blocking
# (`continue-on-error: true`); flip that to enforcing once this list is
# accurate.
#
# Known gaps in sigstore-tuf that likely need entries here until implemented:
#   * succinct (hash-bin) delegations
#   * multi-root-keys / unusual key-type handling beyond ecdsa/ed25519/rsa
